data.description: Welcome home!!!! This stunning property is a perfect blend of comfort and luxury. This spacious property offers 5 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, providing plenty of room for your family. With a generous backyard and a spacious garage, this home has everything you need.  Located in the Wildhorse community, it's close to shopping, walking distance to local elementary school and restaurants. Refrigerator, water softener stay with home.
